name: Thule Child Carrier Cargo Rack 2 - Children
description: Boost the capacity of your Thule® double child carrier with this cargo rack. (Although it’s a tempting rooftop seat, the cargo rack is meant for lightweight, inanimate objects only.)Adds 2.3kg of carrying capacity.Cargo secures with elastic straps or mesh cover.Quick-release clips allow for easy installation or removal.Includes a pocket with a full-width zipper for quick access to snacks, keys or phone.Pocket has a headphone port, making music easily accessible.
